lead_paragraph: PSV Eindhoven retained the Dutch league title after rivals Ajax Amsterdam blew their chance when they failed to beat second-bottom De Graafschap in a dramatic final round of matches on Sunday.

headline.print_headline: PSV Retain Title as Ajax Falter on Dramatic Final Day
